Hi Raefaella,

Here is the email that our Privacy team had sent you in July and on 28 Augu=
st.

The link below you can copy paste into your web browser and it should work.=
 The link has the files you had requested originally.

Kind regards,

Zach

From: Privacy <Privacy@tower.co.nz<mailto:Privacy@tower.co.nz>>
Sent: Thursday, 28 August 2025 11:12 am
To: 'raffaellanz@icloud.com' <raffaellanz@icloud.com<mailto:raffaellanz@icl=
oud.com>>
Cc: Megan Jensen <Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz<mailto:Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz>>
Subject: FW: Privacy Request

Dear Raffaella,

Documents

We have included the documents as requested.

The documents are released to you on the basis that it contains personal in=
formation that you are entitled to receive under the Privacy Act 2020.  Due=
 to the confidential nature of that information, Tower requires that you do=
 not disclose the information provided to you by Tower=E2=80=99s staff to a=
ny third parties, without Tower=E2=80=99s prior written consent.

Note that if the personal information held by Tower is incorrect, you may r=
equest correction of that information.

If you have any further questions or concerns, please contact us on 0800 80=
8 808.

Please use the link below to get access
https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sc393b8aa6fe64f69b68334ef28b2cb7a


Zach Pion
