From: Claims
Sent: Tuesday, September 2, 2025 11:29 AM
To: Raffaella del Prete <raffaellanz@icloud.com>
Subject: RE: REFUND Request : Contents Tower Claim: C90306256

Good afternoon, Raffaella.

It was good talking to you today.

To recap our conversation.

  *   You will receive the contents settlement in three to five days
  *   You will receive the stress benefit payment of $2,000 in the same tim=
e period.
  *   You are to send us your vet fee and report for the cats being hurt fr=
om the claimed event.
  *   I will update you on a monthly basis at the beginning of each month.
  *   You would like your claim file from the date of loss to today to be s=
ent to you. I will get this actioned for you.
  *   You will send me privacy requests for new information we have on file=
 including new claim notes from today onwards.

Kind regards,

Zach

