<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">Dear Raffaella,<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">Documents<o:p></o:p></span><=
/b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">We have included the documents =
as requested.&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">The documents are released to y=
ou on the basis that it contains personal information that you are entitled=
 to receive under the Privacy Act 2020.&nbsp; Due to the confidential natur=
e of that information, Tower requires that
 you do not disclose the information provided to you by Tower=E2=80=99s sta=
ff to any third parties, without Tower=E2=80=99s prior written consent.<o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">Note that if the personal infor=
mation held by Tower is incorrect, you may request correction of that infor=
mation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">If you have any further questio=
ns or concerns, please contact us on 0800 808 808.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
