<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon, Raf=
faella.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">It was good talking=
 to you today.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To recap our conver=
sation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0in" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will receive the contents settle=
ment in three to five days<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagr=
aph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-=
size:11.0pt">You will receive the stress benefit payment of $2,000 in the s=
ame time period.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=
=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0p=
t">You are to send us your vet fee and report for the cats being hurt from =
the claimed event.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" sty=
le=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.=
0pt">I will update you on a monthly basis at the beginning of each month.<o=
:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0i=
n;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You would like =
your claim file from the date of loss to today to be sent to you. I will ge=
t this actioned for you.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagrap=
h" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-si=
ze:11.0pt">You will send me privacy requests for new information we have on=
 file including new claim notes from today onwards.
<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Kind regards,<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
