<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good morning, Raffa=
ella.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I hope you are well=
 this morning.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will receive th=
e $9,000 temporary accommodation payment in 3 to 5 working days.<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The remaining amoun=
t under the temporary accommodation benefit is $13,820.62<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Is there a time I c=
an contact you this week by phone to finalize your contents claim? the loss=
 schedule provided by Asset Restore to date exceeds your sum insured, which=
 means that the contents is a total
 loss as the total value of the contents damaged or destroyed is greater th=
en the sum insured. I work until 1:30 so let me know when this week suits y=
ou.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have confirmation=
 that your privacy request and the information you requested was emailed to=
 you on the 25/07/25. If you can check this date and let me know if you hav=
e it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding updates, =
I am more then happy to update you on the first of each month, would you pr=
efer monthly contacts from me instead of fortnightly?<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding further c=
laim files, we can send you assessor reports as we receive these from the a=
ssessor. It would be less prudent for us to resend you the entire claim fil=
e each month and not efficient for us
 due to the time it takes to action these we may end up getting assessor re=
ports during this process which means that report may not be added to that =
privacy request.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Future assessor rep=
orts should be the only documents we have that you are not given by the ass=
essor as this would come from us.</span><span style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font=
-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:#001272;mso-ligatures:standard=
contextual">
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
